de.thwildau.model

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.thwildau.model.Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is the basis for happening events. It contains attributes to specify events with particular data. It contains methods to set and get the attributes. The class is using the serializable interface to can be interchanged with the server.
    Since:
    2015-01-12
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Kulla, Just
    See Also:
    Serializable, Serialized Form
